Reasoning: The paper focuses on applying lifted inference to computer vision problems, specifically stereo vision and interactive image segmentation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms and optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the efficiency of handling large amounts of data, which could be relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.GR (Computer Graphics).
